            "text": "Mini Motorways",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is the second child of New Zealand dev team Dinosaur Polo Club, a simple yet massively addicting game about building the roadways that connect a growing city. Building games often have a particularly addicting loop of gameplay and reward and ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Mini Motorways",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is no different, topped by pleasant visuals and a great mixture of challenge and relaxing options.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
