            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " can be played in whatever way the player wants. From a relaxing puzzle that one can take their time with, to a challenging time-sensitive task. It is strong in its simplicity and very much worth the time spent on it - even if said time is as short as a 5 minute drive.",
